-- MOVES-Metlife appoints head of Asia capital and reinsurance strategy 
-- 
-- Thu Jun 26, 2014 06:59AM EDT
-- None



June 26 (Reuters) - Insurer MetLife Inc <MET.N> said it appointed Nigel Knowles as head of capital and reinsurance strategy for Asia.

Knowles, who has served as a principle in Milliman's Asia insurance consulting practice, will join MetLife on July 27 and will be based in Hong Kong. [ID:nBw1MPqQba]